						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up opposite to the temple of Vēṇugōpālasvāmi.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1[3]46, Krōdhi, Śrāvaṇa, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the foundation [of a temple] at Krōsūri-pura, made by a member of the fourth caste.</p>						

						</summary>
